wiki.summary: "Love 119" is a song recorded by South Korean boy group RIIZE. It was released on January 5, 2024 as the group's third single. The track samples izi's "Emergency Room" (Korean: 응급실) from the 2005 South Korean television series Sassy Girl Chun-hyang, and was written by Jeong Da-seul of ARTiffect, ChaMane, Moon Seol-ree and Cho Yun-kyoung, composed by Jason Hahs, Colin Magalong, David Wilson and MZMC & arranged by dwilly and MZMC. Read more on Last.fm.
